<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.3.6">
<l>eytta collōṭī ḷaiyēṅ kiyirumiyi ḷaittuṭalam</l>
<l>pittarp pōlac cittam vēṟāyp pēci yayarāmuṉ</l>
<l>atta ṉentai yāti mūrtti yāḻka ṭalaikkaṭainta</l>
<l>maitta cōti yempe rumāṉ vatari vaṇaṅkutumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Before I swoon, babbling [with my] mind distorted like a madman’s,</l>
<l>Body wearying, coughing phlegm, [and] wailing faltered words,</l>
<l>We will worship at Badarī our great lord, that darkened splendor</l>
<l>Who churned the deep sea, father, our father, the primal form.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
